        Selling by Tender in Brisbane: How It Works and Whether It's Right for You
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Tender is one of three main methods of sale available to Brisbane sellers. It suits some properties well and others poorly. Here's what you need to know to make an informed choice.
      </p>
